</p><p>One min vdo
.
Why Rahul.gandhi proposal of givibg vvpat slip in voter hand is imo senseless.
So this nonsense of give vvpat paper slip in voter hand will be instantly rejected by court.
</p><p><b>And I had communicated this properly to many congress leaders.</b>
</p>
<hr>
<p>So imo, Rahul Gandhi is a FAKE OPPOSITION. He gives lip service against EVM to ensure that anti EVM voters stay with Rahul Gandhi and end up wasting time and energy. And  Rahul Gandhi is giving proposal which will enable ECI to continue VVPAT as is&nbsp;!!!
</p>
